{"tid":142240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老人家真係唔應該學玩電話","createTime":"2017-03-03T14:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T14:21:26.000Z","uid":41257,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe557d7e4b7672425eda73ee3792c438432e5ff","tid":142240,"uid":41257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:56:55.000Z","msg":"早排兩老眼見朋友有得上網睇片聽歌同we7<br />\n係咁追住要我教 幾經辛苦教到有啲成果<br />\n兩老就晚晚玩電話 其實都無乜問題<br />\n但教極佢地都好似唔識用個音量鍵<br />\n依家一個大大聲重覆播緊同一首歌<br />\n一個大大聲咁播緊中共紀錄片<br />\n電視機又開到大大聲<br />\n我就係廳享受緊佢地既三重奏<br />\n有時真係有啲後悔教識佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069e8cf2e1f8d4f8b3eca18da196d4a2d039e912","tid":142240,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"係呀 其實啲廢中都唔應該玩"},{"pid":"972f1917869913dcdaccbada96917f1b2210a6a2","tid":142240,"uid":41257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係呀 其實啲廢中都唔應該玩</blockquote><br />\n無錯 睇埋睇咁多中共啦<br />\n洗晒腦"},{"pid":"4d6cbedb60bcf3bdf4f6de6e962e96600b6ff58a","tid":142240,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:03:48.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f35719f7463ecad8ea0a9388879e455c4d4a513","tid":142240,"uid":41257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:06:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就笑唔出<br />\n晚晚都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ddbe639b5385ca854f30fbb903a75ba24f0e1f","tid":142240,"uid":41257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep